HARDWARE and SOFTWARE characteristics
--------------------------------------------------------------------

  It was compiled with 'AMOS Pro Compiler 2.00 - Europress
  Software Ltd (© 1993)' as an executable file for Workbench.
  To operate properly, the directory or drawer
  MUST include all of the following files:
  - GlowTrack.exe ................... Game executable in Workbench
  - HighScore.GWT ......................... file with scores saved
  - MUSICS (Drawer) ........................ music modules OctaMED
  - LANGUAGES (Drawer) ......... text files "Readme" multilanguage
  - MEDPLAYER.LIBRARY ...................... library music OctaMED
  - History_ITA.txt ..............................................
  - History_Eng.txt ................................ [here I am !]
  If you already have the library for the modules in the drawer 
  OctaMED 'Libs' disk system / boot, then you do not need it
  within the directory of the game.

